---
title: Prawn and Coconut Laksa with charred garlic pak choi
description: A laksa is a saucy, spicy noodle dish that hails from Southeast Asia. Common components include noodles aromatic elements, and toppings such as chicken, prawn or fish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R12_W18_IE_IEQCLF13669-3_Main_R__6high-8bc95d59.jpg
